        dc:description           "Figure 83. Pelidnota rubripennis rubripennis (Burmeister) (male specimen compared with Burmeister's syntype by Ohaus from MLUH). A Dorsal habitus B Lateral habitus C Specimen labels and male genitalia D Male genitalia, lateral view E Male parameres, dorsal view." , "Figure 84. Pelidnota rufipennis Waterhouse (valid name Pelidnota rubripennis [Burmeister]) type female (see \" Type specimens and lectotype designation \" in Methods) from BMNH. A Dorsal habitus B Lateral habitus C Specimen labels." ;
